{
  "page": "Chronicles of Maidenpool",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <i><b>Chronicles of Maidenpool</b></i> is a history of <a href=\"/index.php/Maidenpool\" title=\"Maidenpool\">Maidenpool</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chronicles_of_Maidenpool&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>, Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Norren_(House_Mooton)\" title=\"Norren (House Mooton)\">Norren</a> was the keeper of the text. He recorded the time Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Targaryen\" title=\"Daemon Targaryen\">Daemon Targaryen</a> and his alleged <a href=\"/index.php/Paramour\" title=\"Paramour\">paramour</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonseed\" title=\"Dragonseed\">dragonseed</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Nettles\" title=\"Nettles\">Nettles</a>, spent at Maidenpool as guests of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Manfryd_Mooton\" title=\"Manfryd Mooton\">Manfryd Mooton</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfab16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfab16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chronicles_of_Maidenpool&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfab16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfab16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - Rhaenyra Triumphant.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403151550\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.041 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 113/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8559/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 430/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 17/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 539/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.52 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   36.525      1 -total\n 83.55%   30.517      1 Template:Italic_title\n 12.23%    4.468      1 Template:Ref\n  8.32%    3.038      1 Template:Ref/core\n  3.71%    1.354      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:16136-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403151550 and revision id 318041\n -->\n",
